claim: Flublok is approved for adults 18 years and older
explanation: The image is a partial excerpt of clinical-trial efficacy data and literature references for Flublok and Flublok Quadrivalent (showing attack rates, vaccine efficacy percentages, age subgroups ≥50 and ≥65 years in some studies, and reference citations). It does not include any statement of the approved age indication (e.g. “approved for adults 18 years and older”). Therefore, it does not provide evidence to support the claim about Flublok’s approval for adults 18 years and older.
